<div class=3D"markdown-heading" dir=3D"auto"><h1 tabindex=3D"-1" class=3D"h=
eading-element" dir=3D"auto">ESP32-S3 Pinouts</h1><a id=3D"user-content-esp=
32-s3-pinouts" class=3D"anchor" aria-label=3D"Permalink: ESP32-S3 Pinouts" =
href=3D"https://github.com/atomic14/esp32-s3-pinouts#esp32-s3-pinouts"><svg=
